                        <div class="col-md-9">

                            <p>The A11 Time Attendance Clock has Validite's own software loaded onto it. This software allows communication with Validite's Fingerprint Clock Web Service.</p>

                            <p>The Verification / Identification of an employee's fingerprint is extremely fast as it is processed on a PC as oppossed to the A11 Time Attendance Clock which has a 200Mhz processor.</p>

                            <p>One major difference between our Clocks and our competitors is that we have a <strong>Break Key</strong>. This allows Employees to take breaks and reconcile later with shift times for the day.</p>

                            <p>If for any reason the network is down, The A11 Clock will go offline and start to beep every minute.</p>


